<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    body {
      background: #0a0a0a;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Georgia, serif;
    }
    img {
      width: 260px;
      border: 1px solid #333;
      filter: grayscale(100%);
    }
    .name {
      color: #999;
      font-size: 13px;
      letter-spacing: 6px;
      margin-top: 28px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .quote {
      color: #444;
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      margin-top: 12px;
      font-style: italic;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/a1/Alan_Turing_Aged_16.jpg" alt="Alan Turing">
  <p class="name">Alan Turing</p>
  <p class="quote">在布莱切利，他终结了一场战争。此刻，你找到了他。</p>
</body>
</html>
